of what it points to.</div></span></div><ul class="namespaceItemContentSubItems"></ul></div></div><div id="namespace_deno_lstatsync" class="namespaceItem"><div class="docNodeKindIcon"><div class="text-Function bg-Function/15" title="Function">f</div></div><div class="namespaceItemContent"><a href="./././~/Deno.lstatSync" title="Deno.lstatSync">Deno.lstatSync</a><div class="namespaceItemContentDoc"><span><div data-color-mode="dark" data-light-theme="light" data-dark-theme="dark" class="markdown-body markdown-summary"><p>Synchronously returns a <a href="./././~/Deno.FileInfo"><code>Deno.FileInfo</code></a> for the specified
<code>path</code>. If <code>path</code> is a symlink, information for the symlink will be
returned instead of what it points to.</div></span></div><ul class="namespaceItemContentSubItems"></ul></div></div><div id="namespace_deno_maketempdir" class="namespaceItem"><div class="docNodeKindIcon"><div class="text-Function bg-Function/15" title="Function">f</div></div><div class="namespaceItemContent"><a href="./././~/Deno.makeTempDir" title="Deno.makeTempDir">Deno.makeTempDir</a><div class="namespaceItemContentDoc"><span><div data-color-mode="dark" data-light-theme="light" data-dark-theme="dark" class="markdown-body markdown-summary"><p>Creates a new temporary directory in the default directory for temporary
